<lg><lb n="1"/><l><g ref="#leaf"/> <rs type="subject" key="boule"><w lemma="ὁ">ἡ</w> <w lemma="βουλή">βουλὴ</w></rs> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <w lemma="πᾶς">πᾶσι</w> <w lemma="προσηνής">προς<lb n="2" break="no"/>ηνέα</w> <w lemma="ὅδε">τόνδε</w> <persName key="Menander1" type="attested"><name nymRef="#Μένανδρος">Μένανδρον</name></persName></l><lb n="3"/><l><w lemma="πολύς">πολλῶν</w> <w lemma="ἀντί">ἀντ'</w> <w lemma="ἀγαθός">ἀγαθῶν</w><lb n="4"/><w lemma="ἵστημι">στῆσεν</w> <w lemma="ἀμείβομαι">ἀμειβομένη</w></l><lb n="5"/><l><w lemma="ὅς">ὃς</w> <w lemma="μέγας">μεγάλῃ</w> <w lemma="χαρίεις">χαρίεντα</w> <rs type="subject" key="city"><w lemma="πόλις">πόλι</w></rs><lb n="6"/><w lemma="θρεπτήριος">θρεπτήρια</w> <w lemma="τίς">τίνων</w></l><lb n="7"/><l><w lemma="δασμός">δασμοὺς</w> <w lemma="πραύνω">πρηΰνας</w> <w lemma="πᾶς">πᾶσιν</w><lb n="8"/><w lemma="τίθημι">ἔθηκε</w> <w lemma="φάος">φάος</w> <g ref="#leaf"/></l>
</lg>
</div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>The Council, in exchange for many benefits, set up this <supplied reason="subaudible">statue of</supplied> Menandros, who was affable to all, and who, making a welcome repayment for his rearing to the great city, moderated <supplied reason="subaudible">her</supplied> tribute, and established light for all.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>See discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="III.22" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
